trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of instances of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart" /> class.
This class cannot be inherited.

Each <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart> within the collection represents an extensibility element added to a <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimeMultipartRelatedBinding>, and specifies the MIME type for a corresponding <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart>.
trans-unit.target: 각 <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart> 컬렉션 내에 추가 되는 확장성 요소 나타냅니다는 <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimeMultipartRelatedBinding>, 해당 하는 것에 대 한 MIME 형식을 지정 하 고 <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart>합니다.

trans-unit.source: For more information about specifying protocols for XML Web services, see [[\<topic://cpconbuildingaspnetwebservices>]](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/01dfc27c-c68e-4910-a0aa-5e4c2a766b0c).
trans-unit.target: XML 웹 서비스에 대 한 프로토콜을 지정 하는 방법에 대 한 자세한 내용은 참조 [ [ \<topic://cpconbuildingaspnetwebservices >]](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/01dfc27c-c68e-4910-a0aa-5e4c2a766b0c)합니다.

trans-unit.source: For more information about Web Services Description Language (WSDL), see the specification at http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/.
trans-unit.target: 자세한 내용은 대 한 WSDL 웹 서비스 설명 언어 ()에서 사양을 참조 http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart" /> to remove from the collection.
Removes the first occurrence of the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart" /> from the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePartCollection" />.
This method performs a linear search; therefore, the average execution time is proportional to <xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>.

trans-unit.source: The elements that follow the removed `MimePart` move up to occupy the vacated spot.
trans-unit.target: 제거 된 다음에 오는 `MimePart` 위로 이동 하 여 빈된 자리를 채웁니다.
